#: ../../../source/docs/compiling/GitLab.rst:5
msgid "Building and Deploying on GitLab"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../source/docs/compiling/GitLab.rst:7
msgid ""
"`GitLab CI/CD <https://about.gitlab.com/product/continuous-integration/>`_ "
"is a popular continuous integration service which offers free plans to "
"everyone. Thanks to an `Alpine Linux package by Jakub Jirutka <https://pkgs."
"alpinelinux.org/packages?name=emscripten>`_ installing emscripten in GitLab "
"CI/CD is literally a one line task."
msgstr ""

